            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;But &lt;code&gt;data.read().splitlines()&lt;/code&gt; is much easier to read, and memory is not always a concern compared to ease of reading the code.&lt;/span&gt;

